<F P=106> [Article by I.N. Chaushev, Professor N.O. Milanov, S.T. </F>
Tsygankova and N.I. Akimova (Plastic and Reconstructive 
Microsurgery Department (headed by Professor N.O. Milanov), 
NTsKh [expansion not given] (Director ), RAMN [Russian Academy 
